<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 12:55:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普家族的加密项目让投资者厌倦了“获胜”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-23/trump-family-crypto-projects-make-investors-tired-of-winning</link><description>与特朗普家族相关的加密货币公司——曾经表现出色——现在正陷入困境。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEL5CvJ0iDbM/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 21:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-23/trump-family-crypto-projects-make-investors-tired-of-winning</guid></item><item><title>随着加密货币的魔力让黄金支付利息，死去的资产苏醒了</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/crypto-repackages-age-old-jeweler-wisdom-to-give-gold-a-yield</link><description>长期以来，珠宝商一直使用一种简单的机制来保护自己免受金价波动的影响——借入贵金属而不是直接购买。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixF5qyd1W32k/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/crypto-repackages-age-old-jeweler-wisdom-to-give-gold-a-yield</guid></item><item><title>班克曼-弗里德称家长提出了建议，但没有写动议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/bankman-fried-says-parents-made-suggestions-didn-t-write-motion</link><description>FTX 联合创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 告诉法官，他的法学教授父母只是提出了改进他提交的寻求新审判的法庭文件的建议——这位曾经的加密之王现在正在撤回这一请求。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itrIt63B8vJ8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 23:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/bankman-fried-says-parents-made-suggestions-didn-t-write-motion</guid></item><item><title>据称区块链资本将寻求 7 亿美元的新资金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/blockchain-capital-said-to-seek-700-million-for-two-new-funds</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，投资加密货币的风险投资公司 Blockchain Capital 正在为两只新基金筹集 7 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/inbbwnQssrok/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 22:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/blockchain-capital-said-to-seek-700-million-for-two-new-funds</guid></item><item><title>比特币因对特朗普延长伊朗停火的乐观情绪而上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/bitcoin-rises-on-optimism-over-trump-s-extended-iran-ceasefire</link><description>周三，在唐纳德·特朗普总统表示将延长与伊朗的停火协议后，比特币与股市一起上涨，触及一月份以来的最高水平，提振了市场信心。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWl21yVTKObg/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 05:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/bitcoin-rises-on-optimism-over-trump-s-extended-iran-ceasefire</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行行长西波隆并不担心数字欧元投票的延迟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/ecb-s-cipollone-not-worried-about-delay-of-digital-euro-vote</link><description>欧洲央行执行委员会皮耶罗·西波隆 (Piero Cipollone) 不太担心欧洲议会对数字欧元项目的关键投票可能从 5 月初推迟到 6 月中旬。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iG9WUBq1P9UA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 13:57:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/ecb-s-cipollone-not-worried-about-delay-of-digital-euro-vote</guid></item></channel></rss>